  {% endif %}

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="mx-auto text-center font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance text-waikawa-gray-900 text-5xl">
        We have worked with thousands of amazing people
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 grid-rows-1 gap-8 text-base/6 text-waikawa-gray-900 sm:mt-20 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:mx-0 xl:max-w-none xl:grid-flow-col xl:grid-cols-4">
      {# Testimonial 1 #}
      <figure class="rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-lg ring-1 ring-gray-900/5 sm:col-span-2 xl:col-start-2 xl:row-end-1">
        <blockquote class="p-6 text-lg font-normal tracking-tight text-waikawa-gray-900 sm:p-12 sm:text-xl/8">
          <p>“It's been a night and day difference switching from our paid ad management from our previous vendor to Eva. She helps us tell the story of ROI that our ads are making and we have seen an improvement in high quality sales leads come through our ads since she has taken over. I especially like that she is hands-on with building the reports between software to help visually show the positive impact.”</p>
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-4 border-t border-gray-900/10 px-6 py-4 sm:flex-nowrap">
          <img src="/assets/images/testimonials/mackenzie.jpeg" alt="" class="size-10 flex-none rounded-full bg-gray-50"/>
          <div class="flex-auto">
            <div class="font-semibold text-waikawa-gray-900">Mackenzie Hesler</div>
            <div class="text-gray-600">Growth Marketing Manager</div>
          </div>
          <img src="/assets/images/clients/lifelabs.png" alt="" class="h-10 w-auto flex-none"/>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
      <div class="space-y-8 xl:contents xl:space-y-0">
        {# Column 1 #}
        <div class="space-y-8 xl:row-span-2">
          {# Testimonial 2 #}
          <figure class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-lg ring-1 ring-gray-900/5">
            <blockquote class="text-waikawa-gray-900">
              <p>“Eva possesses qualities that set her apart from most other agencies - namely, accountability and ownership. Her proficiency in assuming responsibility for and executing our paid acquisition channels has been pivotal to our inbound success. Her unwavering commitment and ability to manage an entire campaign amidst constant change requests from diverse stakeholders have been truly remarkable. In need of someone to seamlessly integrate into your marketing team? Look no further than Eva. I wholeheartedly endorse her for any company, regardless of size, seeking to revitalize their paid acquisition campaigns!”</p>
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-4">
              <img src="/assets/images/testimonials/sean.jpeg" alt="" class="size-10 rounded-full bg-gray-50"/>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-waikawa-gray-900">Sean Syal</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600">Director, Growth Marketing at Coursedog</div>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>

          {# Testimonial 3 #}
          <figure class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-lg ring-1 ring-gray-900/5">
            <blockquote class="text-waikawa-gray-900">
              <p>“Eva's a true professional who makes work fun. In a challenging year, she was able to learn about the nuances of our industry and target market, and ramp up our digital impact - all at an impressive pace. A thoughtful strategist and effective executor, she's been invaluable to our team and marketing efforts.”</p>
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-4">
              <img src="/assets/images/testimonials/ashley_wide.jpeg" alt="" class="size-10 rounded-full bg-gray-50"/>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-waikawa-gray-900">Ashley Hargreaves</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600">VP Marketing at Canalyst</div>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
