          {# Testimonial 6 #}
          <figure class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-lg ring-1 ring-gray-900/5">
            <blockquote class="text-waikawa-gray-900">
              <p>“Working with Eva has been fantastic. Her attention to detail and management of our ad accounts has been very beneficial. She provides detailed reporting and is always there if you need her. We have been able to figure out our CPA and the best strategies to get more leads. I highly recommend her services.”</p>
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-4">
              <img src="/assets/images/testimonials/mike_wide.jpg" alt="" class="size-10 rounded-full bg-gray-50"/>
              <div>
