          {# Testimonial 10 #}
          <figure class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-lg ring-1 ring-gray-900/5">
            <blockquote class="text-waikawa-gray-900">
              <p>“Eva is such a pleasure to work with! Her knowledge, enthusiasm, and passion light up the boardroom. She is a master at developing PPC campaigns and implementing measurable strategies. She is always the first one to point out the weak points of any advertising campaign, which makes everything she touches better and stronger. Eva also is so professional when handling client objections or questions. I would hire Eva immediately if you need an online advertising specialist. Thank you for everything!”</p>
